title: This Place is Awful!!
body: i took my son here and he died!!! I will eat your burgers no more!!!! My cat also died and my house burnt down. I have diarrhea and migraines and i cant feel any of my limbs..... i have been hospitalized and my wife left me!!

ownersResponse.body: Hi Bob! Iâ€™m sorry to hear that! I hope he gets better soon. You and your remaining family are entitled to a free pack of breadsticks on your next visit. Check your email for the coupon code!

title: terrible, what happened??
body: I used to go here back in the day all the time. What happened? the food quality is really bad, and there's a weird stink coming from the locked back room, and there's this gross darkish liquid near it. I'd much rather eat at mcwonalds at this point!

title: Wretched, terrible, disgusting place
body: I've had the absolute worst parts of my life in this disgusting establishment. I think the world would be better if this place spontaneously burst into flames. God willing I will never see this place or you ever again.

title: Good stuff!
body: Brought the family here to relax! The service was terrific and the yogurt is like nothing else in this town! Lots of memories made here!

title: Great food! Kids loved it
body: Took my kids here for a birthday party. The town never had a McWonalds so this was a new experience for us! We only had that other burger place but its quality has been going down for a while.
